WEBVTT

00:00.050 --> 00:01.861
What is the best thing about being married?

00:04.273 --> 00:05.351
How do I say it?

00:05.460 --> 00:06.084
Hello?

00:06.153 --> 00:07.067
It is the best.

00:08.325 --> 00:09.755
I think that really, at the end of the day, like...

00:10.875 --> 00:12.671
...if you find the right person, it's the best.

00:12.825 --> 00:17.662
It's like life gives you a person and you have to find that person...

00:17.738 --> 00:20.263
...and if you find that person it's like, "Thank god."

00:20.391 --> 00:21.535
And that's kind of how I feel.

